data.description: 5 acres of Horse property complete with a beautiful Cabin style Home, Barn and so much more! This home offers something for everyone! Located 26 miles from the Salt Lake International Airport and Salt Lake City and only 4 miles to Tooele puts you close to anything you could need. Let's begin as you drive down Cimmarron Way, you notice that you are not on top of your neighbors and as you pull up to the house you are not worried if there will be enough parking for your cars, trucks, toys and other trailers you might have. That even includes a 30amp plug for the RV's! You see the unique wood cabin style logs around the whole house with 7 year stain that was just done in 2023. All the fencing around most of the 5 Acres has been replaced so that even the dogs stay in the yard, not just the horses. The solar panels are paid for and stay with the house. They use the Tesla power App to monitor how much power you are gathering at any time. There is a new and beautiful 50' x 50' barn, Horse stalls with rubber floors that have automatic water that is heated for winter, storage and a 24' x 50' shop with power and water. Just outside the barn is your own riding arena! Now let's go inside. As you walk up to the front door you are greeted with the large front porch and nice inviting entry way with Vaulted ceilings through the whole entry and great room areas. The open Kitchen, living room w/ fireplace and dining area are the perfect place to gather. There is a large laundry room/mud room on the main level to help keep the rest of the house clean. There are 2 primary bedrooms to choose from depending on which level of the house you like to sleep on. Have you ever seen a mega-closet before? Well, this trending idea keeps all the clothes close to the laundry room and hunting/skiing and other recreational items next to the garage so you can load up easily and go. You will see what I mean when you come by for a showing or you can look it up on Tik Tok. The basement features an indoor playground, a second fire place, theater, workout room or multi-purpose room that could be a 3rd bedroom, 2 bathrooms, large cold storage, secure storage for things you want to keep safe and an organized storage room for all your seasonal dcor. With this layout it would be easy to set up for Mother-in-law or an ADU. As you head out to the backyard there is roughly a half-acre of yard that has a covered patio, grass areas, play areas, a basketball court, in ground trampoline, an area that is ready for your future playset and even another area set aside that was planned for a future pool. Did I mention that the 12 person Hot Tub is included! There are also water spigots run to the back part of the property for horses, gardening etc. The garden tool shed can also be used for a chicken coop. New walkways have been added to make it easier to get from the house to the barn and other parts of the yard no matter what the weather. This has been set up extremely well so you can optimize the potential of this amazing property! If you are into golfing there is a golf course around the corner. The views from the front or back of the house are amazing! You can see the valley, lake, mountains or even the unique styling of the Tooele Valley Temple from the front porch. Come take in all that this home has to offer not just for you but for your equestrian friends as well. Seller is asking for 1 week possession after closing and if you see some furniture that you like it is more than likely for sale.
